org.influxdata.client

Interface InfluxDBClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InfluxDBClientImpl

    public interface InfluxDBClient
extends AutoCloseable
    The client of theInfluxDB 2.0for Time Series that implements HTTP API defined by Influx API Service swagger.yml.
    Author:
    Jakub Bednar (bednar@github) (11/10/2018 08:56)
